data-triple-N3.o: "Sir Michael Philip "Mick" Jagger (born 26 July 1943) OBE is an English musician, singer, songwriter and actor, best known as the lead vocalist and a founder member of the Rolling Stones. Jagger's career has spanned over 50 years."@en
